import { CardMedia, Container,Grid, TextField, Typography,FormControlLabel,Checkbox, Button } from "@material-ui/core";
import React from "react";
import logo from "../logo.jpeg";
const Report =()=>{
    return(
        <Container>
            <Grid container spacing={2}>
                <Grid item md={12}>
                <CardMedia
                    style={{height: 200, width: "50%"}}
                    component="img"
                    alt="Biossay"
                    height="auto"
                    image={logo}
                />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item md={12}>
                    <Typography variant="h5">REPORTE DE SERVICIO TÉCNICO</Typography>
                </Grid>
                
                <Grid item md={12}>
                    <Typography>INFORMACIÓN DEL CLIENTE</Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item md={6}>
                    <TextField variant="outlined" label="Razón Social" fullWidth />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item md={6}>
                    <TextField variant="outlined" label="Equipo" fullWidth />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item md={6}>
                    <TextField variant="outlined" label="Dirección" fullWidth />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item md={6}>
                    <TextField variant="outlined" label="Modelo" fullWidth />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item md={6}>
                    <TextField variant="outlined" label="Fecha de ultima revisión" fullWidth />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item md={6}>
                    <TextField variant="outlined" label="Nº Serie" fullWidth />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item md={12}>
                    <Typography>TIPO DE SERVICIO</Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item md={4}><FormControlLabel value="1" control={<Checkbox color="primary" />} label="Seguimiento de Equipo" labelPlacement="start" /> </Grid>
                <Grid item md={4}><FormControlLabel value="2" control={<Checkbox color="primary" />} label="Revisión de Equipo" labelPlacement="start" /> </Grid>
                <Grid item md={4}><FormControlLabel value="3" control={<Checkbox color="primary" />} label="Mantenimiento Preventivo" labelPlacement="start" /> </Grid>
                <Grid item md={4}><FormControlLabel value="3" control={<Checkbox color="primary" />} label="Retiro de Equipo" labelPlacement="start" /> </Grid>
                <Grid item md={4}><FormControlLabel value="3" control={<Checkbox color="primary" />} label="Mantenimiento Correctivo" labelPlacement="start" /> </Grid>
                <Grid item md={4}><FormControlLabel value="3" control={<Checkbox color="primary" />} label="Asesoria Cientifica" labelPlacement="start" /> </Grid>
                <Grid item md={4}><FormControlLabel value="3" control={<Checkbox color="primary" />} label="Capacitación" labelPlacement="start" /> </Grid>
                <Grid item md={4}><FormControlLabel value="3" control={<Checkbox color="primary" />} label="Capacitación" labelPlacement="start" /> </Grid>

                
                <Grid item md={12}>
                     <Typography>HALLAZGO</Typography> 
                    <TextField variant="outlined" label="HALLAZGO" multiline rows={5} fullWidth />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item md={12}>
                     <Typography>PROCEDIMIENTO</Typography> 
                    <TextField variant="outlined" label="HALLAZGO" multiline rows={5} fullWidth />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item md={12}>
                     <Typography>POSIBLES CAUSAS</Typography> 
                    <TextField variant="outlined" label="HALLAZGO" multiline rows={5} fullWidth />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item md={12}>
                     <Typography>RECOMENDACIONES</Typography> 
                    <TextField variant="outlined" label="HALLAZGO" multiline rows={5} fullWidth />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item md={12}>
                     <Typography>OBSERVACIONES</Typography> 
                    <TextField variant="outlined" label="HALLAZGO" multiline rows={5} fullWidth />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item md={12}>
                     <Typography>OPERATIVIDAD</Typography> 
                     <Typography>El equipo queda en las siguientes condiciones:</Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item md={4}>
                <FormControlLabel
                        value="start"
                        control={<Checkbox color="primary" />}
                        label="Operativo"
                        labelPlacement="start"
                        />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item md={4}>
                <FormControlLabel
                        value="start"
                        control={<Checkbox color="primary" />}
                        label="No Operativo"
                        labelPlacement="start"
                        />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item md={4}>
                <FormControlLabel
                        value="start"
                        control={<Checkbox color="primary" />}
                        label="En Seguimiento"
                        labelPlacement="start"
                        />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item md={4}>
                    <Button variant="contained" style={{color:"white"}} color="primary">
                        Guardar
                    </Button>
                </Grid>
            </Grid>
        </Container>
    );
}

export default Report;
